WEBVTT

01:32.130 --> 01:34.990
[How dare you!?]

01:35.030 --> 01:38.030
[Episode 19]

02:01.310 --> 02:02.240
What does it say?

02:04.040 --> 02:05.100
It's Yan language.

02:06.790 --> 02:09.190
The Emperor
is going to Mount Bei tomorrow.

02:10.360 --> 02:11.840
Someone wants to kill you.

02:12.750 --> 02:15.210
You can leave the city
through the west gate.

02:15.960 --> 02:17.160
Could our identities

02:17.240 --> 02:18.300
have been exposed?

02:19.450 --> 02:22.110
Does he know
we're planning to kill the Emperor?

02:25.960 --> 02:27.090
That's impossible.

02:27.470 --> 02:28.670
If that were the case,

02:29.829 --> 02:30.840
how could we still be

02:30.840 --> 02:32.450
safe here at the posthouse?

02:33.630 --> 02:34.430
Could there be

02:35.430 --> 02:37.560
other compatriots hiding in the city,

02:37.960 --> 02:39.030
quietly aiding us?

02:39.560 --> 02:41.870
Or is this some kind of trap?

02:48.800 --> 02:56.560
[Capital of Xia]

03:06.810 --> 03:10.550
[Zhao Wucheng,
Commander of the Imperial Guards]

03:30.280 --> 03:30.810
Hurry up!

03:31.190 --> 03:31.650
Keep up!

03:33.120 --> 03:33.660
Hurry!

03:38.240 --> 03:40.300
They withdrew many Imperial Guards.

03:40.470 --> 03:41.600
The Imperial Guards

03:41.870 --> 03:43.870
are the Emperor's personal troops.

03:45.079 --> 03:47.310
Pulling out so many at once?

03:48.750 --> 03:49.610
Could it be that

03:50.200 --> 03:52.260
Xiahou Dan really went to Mount Bei?

03:52.750 --> 03:53.960
Then aside from the Emperor,

03:53.960 --> 03:55.490
who else would want us dead?

03:57.190 --> 03:59.120
The people of Great Xia are treacherous.

03:59.120 --> 04:00.450
We don't know if the note

04:00.680 --> 04:02.120
is true or false.

04:10.800 --> 04:12.200
Let's wait a bit longer.

04:29.560 --> 04:30.390
Stop the carriage!

04:30.390 --> 04:30.920
Stop!

04:34.430 --> 04:34.920
Well...

04:37.830 --> 04:39.230
My Lord, are you alright?

04:41.680 --> 04:42.210
I'm fine.

04:47.120 --> 04:47.690
Did...

04:48.730 --> 04:49.680
Did something

04:49.680 --> 04:50.680
just rush past?

04:51.040 --> 04:51.680
Did it?

04:52.390 --> 04:53.650
I didn't see anything.

04:53.680 --> 04:54.810
This forest is huge.

04:55.000 --> 04:56.730
It was probably a small animal.

04:57.560 --> 04:58.090
Alright.

04:58.720 --> 04:59.250
Let's go.

05:00.160 --> 05:01.360
Steady the carriage.

05:01.430 --> 05:01.750
Yes.

05:10.490 --> 05:11.020
Let's go.

05:18.040 --> 05:18.830
Your Highness,

05:18.830 --> 05:19.560
at Mount Bei,

05:19.600 --> 05:22.000
Lord Cao has already made arrangements
with his men.

05:22.000 --> 05:25.260
As for Lord Mu, he's on his way
to the posthouse with his men.

05:26.360 --> 05:27.120
Thank you.

05:28.070 --> 05:28.800
Please, sit.

05:35.630 --> 05:36.120
Stop.

05:55.980 --> 05:56.440
My Lord,

05:56.710 --> 05:58.240
they have all left the city.

05:58.430 --> 05:59.340
Great.

06:00.750 --> 06:01.640
Remember,

06:01.920 --> 06:03.870
make a big scene later.

06:04.540 --> 06:05.240
Do you understand?

06:05.240 --> 06:05.560
Yes.

06:07.680 --> 06:08.680
Once it's done,

06:09.240 --> 06:11.190
Her Majesty will reward you generously.

06:11.190 --> 06:12.120
I should thank Her Majesty.

06:12.120 --> 06:13.180
Thank you, My Lord.

06:20.000 --> 06:20.480
Move!

06:21.720 --> 06:22.280
Move!

06:27.230 --> 06:31.020
[Yixuan Inn]

06:28.360 --> 06:29.950
Hurry up and get out of the way!

06:29.950 --> 06:31.240
By order of the Empress Dowager.

06:31.240 --> 06:32.950
The envoy delegation
has violated the laws of Great Xia

06:32.950 --> 06:34.480
and endangered the safety of its people.

06:34.480 --> 06:36.390
They are to be arrested immediately!

06:36.390 --> 06:37.350
On His Majesty's command, we're here...

06:37.350 --> 06:38.240
Anyone who resists

06:38.240 --> 06:39.840
will be executed on the spot!

06:48.430 --> 06:49.760
The letter was right.

06:50.070 --> 06:51.470
Someone wants to kill us.

06:51.560 --> 06:53.960
The Emperor's soldiers are fighting them.

06:54.159 --> 06:55.020
Your Highness,

06:55.159 --> 06:57.020
should we charge out in the chaos?

06:57.800 --> 06:59.000
How many of them are here?

06:59.000 --> 07:00.030
Several dozen.

07:07.120 --> 07:09.850
The people of Great Xia
truly underestimated us.

07:10.190 --> 07:11.520
They think these few men

07:11.720 --> 07:13.310
are enough to kill us all.

07:15.270 --> 07:15.800
It's hot.

07:17.270 --> 07:18.530
Let it cool down first.

07:19.000 --> 07:20.260
Once we deal with them,

07:20.920 --> 07:22.920
we'll come back and drink it slowly.

07:27.780 --> 07:29.290
[Yixuan Inn]

07:30.230 --> 07:30.520
[Yixuan Inn]

07:31.020 --> 07:31.540
[Yixuan Inn]

08:11.160 --> 08:12.910
[Yixuan Inn]

08:21.160 --> 08:21.620
Lord Wu.

08:27.160 --> 08:28.020
Your Highness.

08:31.020 --> 08:33.020
[Tu'er has extraordinary combat skills]

08:33.020 --> 08:35.030
[Most of the assassins were killed or
injured. The plan went smoothly]

08:35.960 --> 08:36.669
Excellent.

08:38.330 --> 08:41.590
He truly deserves his title
as the top fighter in Yan State.

08:44.570 --> 08:52.240
[Yixuan Inn]

08:53.600 --> 08:55.800
Sir, your martial skill is formidable.

08:56.030 --> 08:56.630
Thank you.

09:00.000 --> 09:00.730
Satisfying!

09:01.030 --> 09:02.590
We killed so many people of Great Xia.

09:02.590 --> 09:05.990
Let's see how that old
Emperor of Yan can still talk peace now.

09:06.480 --> 09:07.630
Yan delegation?

09:18.000 --> 09:18.860
Your Highness,

09:18.980 --> 09:20.240
what should we do next?

09:23.320 --> 09:24.780
Change into their clothes

09:25.370 --> 09:26.700
and take their weapons.

09:28.080 --> 09:28.690
We

09:30.550 --> 09:31.810
are going to Mount Bei!

09:38.550 --> 09:40.350
A light rain comes from the east,

09:41.320 --> 09:43.100
carried by a fair wind.

09:46.150 --> 09:47.390
It seems this rain

09:48.390 --> 09:50.360
is inevitable.

09:50.930 --> 09:53.950
[Capital of Xia]

09:58.480 --> 09:59.160
Who are you?

09:59.640 --> 10:02.290
[Token]

10:00.080 --> 10:01.320
We are acting under orders

10:01.320 --> 10:02.320
to leave the city.

10:10.290 --> 10:10.820
Make way.

10:11.940 --> 10:12.840
[Token]

10:12.080 --> 10:12.880
Let them pass.

10:27.480 --> 10:28.100
Lord Zhao.

10:28.510 --> 10:29.310
I have already

10:29.480 --> 10:30.410
let those people

10:30.960 --> 10:31.960
out of the city.

10:37.750 --> 10:39.210
Who are you talking about?

10:40.240 --> 10:40.700
My Lord,

10:41.120 --> 10:42.850
I followed your order and...

10:44.870 --> 10:46.840
I only gave one order today.

10:47.270 --> 10:49.750
That was to guard the gate as usual.

10:50.630 --> 10:51.430
Do you hear me?

10:52.360 --> 10:52.720
Yes.

11:12.340 --> 11:13.940
Watch the situation closely

11:14.000 --> 11:16.060
and report any developments at once.

11:18.000 --> 11:19.910
My Lord, are you worried...

11:23.480 --> 11:25.740
You never put all your eggs in one basket.

11:27.910 --> 11:29.390
Only Heaven knows

11:31.730 --> 11:33.990
whether today we'll save the Emperor...

11:35.600 --> 11:37.450
or be too late.

11:53.750 --> 11:55.960
A ceasefire and trade
between Yan and Great Xia

11:55.960 --> 11:57.390
does Prince Duan no harm.

11:58.360 --> 11:59.480
No matter how you look at it,

11:59.480 --> 12:01.940
he has no reason
to sabotage the peace talks.

12:02.720 --> 12:04.960
So what detail have I missed?

12:05.600 --> 12:07.200
Your Highness, don't worry.

12:07.200 --> 12:08.750
His Majesty said if there's an emergency,

12:08.750 --> 12:10.550
he will send someone to tell you.

12:10.840 --> 12:12.320
Has Consort Xie
shown any unusual behavior?

12:12.320 --> 12:14.380
Consort Xie has been in her courtyard

12:14.790 --> 12:15.670
all morning.

12:41.910 --> 12:44.670
She's been burning paper offerings
for her unborn child.

12:44.670 --> 12:46.470
She's burning them very slowly.

12:46.510 --> 12:48.440
It's more like she's toasting them

12:48.910 --> 12:49.970
than burning them.

12:52.390 --> 12:54.120
Roasting them... with fire?

12:59.120 --> 13:02.610
[All is as usual.
Prince Duan advocates peace talks]

13:01.200 --> 13:01.630
Yes.

13:02.440 --> 13:03.480
How could I forget?

13:02.610 --> 13:06.400
[I'm being watched]

13:04.080 --> 13:06.880
Xie Yong'er used this trick
in the original story.

13:12.120 --> 13:14.170
[I'm being watched.
His Majesty is in danger at Mount Bei]

13:12.630 --> 13:13.690
I'm being watched.

13:14.170 --> 13:16.230
[The Yan people
are attempting an assassination]

13:14.360 --> 13:15.670
His Majesty is in danger at Mount Bei.

13:15.670 --> 13:18.400
The Yan people
are attempting an assassination.

13:30.360 --> 13:34.910
[Kunyu Palace]

13:31.910 --> 13:32.960
Consort Xie,

13:33.510 --> 13:35.320
you haven't fully recovered yet.

13:35.320 --> 13:37.600
His Highness has repeatedly instructed us.

13:37.600 --> 13:39.860
You should return inside and rest early.

13:42.510 --> 13:44.270
You've been doing this all morning.

13:44.270 --> 13:45.730
At a time like this,

13:46.000 --> 13:48.400
please don't make things difficult for me.

13:58.700 --> 14:00.220
[Token]

14:04.960 --> 14:06.030
Thank you, Eunuch.

14:08.150 --> 14:09.440
Then I'll trouble you

14:09.590 --> 14:10.910
to help me

14:10.910 --> 14:12.170
clean these things up.

14:13.650 --> 14:21.970
[Kunyu Palace]

14:13.870 --> 14:15.320
Ling, let's go back inside.

14:15.320 --> 14:15.670
Yes.

14:25.030 --> 14:26.960
Your Highness, what's wrong with you?

14:26.960 --> 14:28.770
Wake up! Your Highness!

14:29.240 --> 14:30.100
Your Highness!

14:50.290 --> 14:52.510
[Token]

14:54.000 --> 14:55.390
Your Highness,
word has come from the city.

14:55.390 --> 14:56.320
The Yan people killed the guards

14:56.320 --> 14:58.520
and their whereabouts are now unknown.

15:01.530 --> 15:03.120
Prepare a secret guard outfit for me.

15:03.120 --> 15:04.120
We're leaving the city.

15:04.120 --> 15:05.250
Why, Your Highness?

15:05.270 --> 15:07.000
The Yan people are heading to Mount Bei
to assassinate His Majesty.

15:07.000 --> 15:09.080
Prince Duan's men
are secretly aiding them.

15:09.080 --> 15:10.270
We're going to save His Majesty.

15:10.270 --> 15:11.130
Your Highness,

15:11.150 --> 15:12.080
His Majesty told us

15:12.080 --> 15:13.000
that if there is any danger,

15:13.000 --> 15:13.870
we are to protect you

15:13.870 --> 15:15.320
and ensure you do not leave the palace.

15:15.320 --> 15:17.080
The mountain must be crawling
with Prince Duan's men.

15:17.080 --> 15:18.750
Besides, you don't know martial arts.

15:18.750 --> 15:20.950
Even if you go there, it would be in vain.

15:22.720 --> 15:24.850
Can you mobilize the Imperial Guards?

15:25.000 --> 15:25.960
Only Prince Duan can do it.

15:25.960 --> 15:27.220
That's what I thought.

15:28.000 --> 15:29.240
Zhao Wucheng,
Commander of the Imperial Guards,

15:29.240 --> 15:30.910
has already been bought over
by Prince Duan.

15:30.910 --> 15:32.170
If we report it rashly,

15:32.320 --> 15:33.580
it will only alert him.

15:33.750 --> 15:35.150
There's no time to worry about that now.

15:35.150 --> 15:36.680
Bring out what we prepared.

15:39.370 --> 15:40.230
Your Highness,

15:40.320 --> 15:41.450
Consort Xie sent someone to deliver this.

15:40.770 --> 15:44.950
[Token]

15:45.600 --> 15:46.380
Xie Yong'er?

15:47.340 --> 15:48.100
That's it.

15:48.700 --> 15:50.200
You stay in the palace
and protect Consort Xie.

15:50.200 --> 15:51.800
The rest of you, come with me.

16:32.080 --> 16:34.880
The surroundings here
are indeed quite pleasant.

16:35.480 --> 16:37.080
I am glad you like it, Mother.

16:38.390 --> 16:39.630
Heaven bestows
the Five Virtues upon our people,

16:39.630 --> 16:41.750
including a mother's kindness
and a son's filial devotion.

16:41.750 --> 16:44.150
Now that the rain falls
to bless all things,

16:44.150 --> 16:46.180
it is all thanks to Your Majesties.

16:49.490 --> 16:50.610
Walk with me.

17:22.680 --> 17:23.609
Are you alright?

17:26.190 --> 17:28.390
There are soldiers hiding in the woods.

17:28.530 --> 17:31.460
They were already there
when we went up the mountain.

17:31.480 --> 17:33.880
It's a good thing
Wanyin didn't come along.

17:34.000 --> 17:35.330
Did you bring the thing?

17:47.590 --> 17:49.550
What lovely weather.

18:01.030 --> 18:04.420
Son, you attend to countless affairs
and keep the realm in your heart.

18:04.260 --> 18:09.940
[Be Remembered with Honor for All Ages]

18:04.960 --> 18:06.290
Despite such busyness,

18:06.720 --> 18:10.070
you still took the time
to inspect my mausoleum with me.

18:10.790 --> 18:12.750
I'm deeply moved.

18:13.830 --> 18:14.650
Look.

18:15.030 --> 18:16.070
Mount Bei

18:16.830 --> 18:18.270
has pleasant scenery.

18:18.720 --> 18:21.350
This mausoleum is quite magnificent.

18:22.400 --> 18:23.160
Son,

18:23.790 --> 18:24.920
you are thoughtful.

18:25.480 --> 18:26.160
All of this

18:27.000 --> 18:28.550
is simply my duty.

18:32.510 --> 18:33.480
Indeed.

18:36.550 --> 18:37.640
My son

18:38.590 --> 18:40.110
lingers in the harem

18:40.790 --> 18:43.640
and busies himself
with the affairs of Great Xia.

18:44.550 --> 18:45.440
Now

18:46.110 --> 18:47.510
he even has to worry about

18:47.680 --> 18:49.080
matters of other states.

18:50.110 --> 18:51.860
Your duties truly

18:52.790 --> 18:54.720
are too many.

19:03.510 --> 19:06.110
I can't help but worry for you.

19:10.910 --> 19:14.500
[Be Remembered with Honor for All Ages]

19:11.590 --> 19:13.000
His Majesty's choice

19:13.270 --> 19:14.660
of Mount Bei as the site

19:14.960 --> 19:16.690
shows his remarkable insight.

19:17.200 --> 19:19.130
And with your abundant blessings,

19:19.430 --> 19:21.070
it is a perfect match.

19:21.540 --> 19:23.680
Such maternal kindness and filial devotion

19:23.680 --> 19:25.000
are a blessing

19:28.000 --> 19:29.460
to the people of Great Xia.

19:30.130 --> 19:34.890
[Be Remembered with Honor for All Ages]

19:30.310 --> 19:31.680
As long as my son is here,

19:32.590 --> 19:35.490
of course it is a blessing
to the people of Great Xia.

19:38.500 --> 19:39.500
It's just that...

19:42.310 --> 19:43.830
Now you've grown up,

19:44.590 --> 19:45.790
you have more and more

19:46.920 --> 19:48.510
ideas of your own.

19:49.610 --> 19:50.720
While

19:51.350 --> 19:53.110
I'm pleased,

19:53.680 --> 19:55.740
I'm actually more worried about you.

19:56.350 --> 19:57.030
Mother,

19:57.920 --> 19:59.000
why do you say that?

19:59.790 --> 20:00.810
Do you remember

20:01.750 --> 20:02.960
Shanyi, the dancer?

20:04.120 --> 20:06.180
The one who tried to assassinate you.

20:10.030 --> 20:10.670
Alright.

20:11.110 --> 20:12.440
Let's not talk about it.

20:13.200 --> 20:14.000
It's just that

20:15.110 --> 20:17.240
there's one thing I don't understand.

20:17.240 --> 20:18.350
Didn't that incident

20:18.350 --> 20:20.590
already teach you a lesson?

20:21.590 --> 20:24.000
Yet in what you've been doing
these past few days,

20:24.000 --> 20:26.530
I see signs of you
repeating the same mistake.

20:31.120 --> 20:32.170
Shanyi...

20:32.920 --> 20:35.580
was originally sent here
as a dancer to perform.

20:36.750 --> 20:38.010
Why did she stay

20:38.750 --> 20:40.150
and become my concubine?

20:40.960 --> 20:41.880
And why did she

20:42.880 --> 20:44.070
attempt to assassinate me
at the cost of her own life

20:44.070 --> 20:45.270
when she knew

20:46.720 --> 20:48.050
it could never succeed?

20:49.510 --> 20:50.770
Others might not know,

20:51.640 --> 20:52.300
but Mother,

20:54.070 --> 20:55.030
don't you know?

20:56.220 --> 20:57.480
What are you implying?

20:58.000 --> 20:59.350
What I mean is that

21:01.000 --> 21:02.530
a ceasefire and peace talks

21:02.900 --> 21:05.250
benefit the people of Great Xia.

21:06.000 --> 21:06.830
Why are you

21:07.550 --> 21:08.950
so unwilling to allow it?

21:17.160 --> 21:18.400
Yan State

21:19.190 --> 21:21.120
lies in a harsh and barbarous land.

21:21.720 --> 21:22.240
They are

21:22.720 --> 21:24.100
bloodthirsty

21:24.310 --> 21:25.500
and incorrigible.

21:25.920 --> 21:26.980
You saw it yourself

21:27.270 --> 21:28.920
at the Grand Longevity Banquet.

21:28.920 --> 21:31.400
Their greedy eyes and wild ambitions

21:31.400 --> 21:32.800
were clear for all to see.

21:34.400 --> 21:34.920
Son,

21:35.750 --> 21:37.400
surely you saw that too.

21:40.160 --> 21:40.830
Thank you

21:42.000 --> 21:43.460
for your concern, Mother.

21:44.290 --> 21:50.990
[Be Remembered with Honor for All Ages]

21:44.750 --> 21:45.590
Forget it.

21:47.240 --> 21:48.270
Let's say no more.

21:49.270 --> 21:51.070
There is no point in saying more.

21:51.310 --> 21:55.240
I only hope the young Crown Prince doesn't
take after your temperament

21:55.400 --> 21:57.120
and grow so stubborn.

22:00.070 --> 22:00.670
By the way,

22:01.640 --> 22:02.480
yesterday,

22:03.590 --> 22:06.400
the young Crown Prince
mentioned you to me.

22:06.770 --> 22:07.580
He said

22:07.750 --> 22:09.160
he missed his father.

22:10.790 --> 22:11.510
Go away!

22:12.200 --> 22:13.000
Your Majesty,

22:13.680 --> 22:16.010
this is a reward from the Empress Dowager.

22:17.830 --> 22:19.640
Whether Xiahou Dan cooperates or not...

22:19.640 --> 22:20.200
Don't come over!

22:20.200 --> 22:21.070
He must give me...

22:21.070 --> 22:21.440
Go away.

22:21.440 --> 22:22.920
A Crown Prince.

22:23.350 --> 22:25.210
Congratulations, Your Majesty.

22:26.240 --> 22:27.810
From this day on,

22:28.590 --> 22:30.790
he shall be the one and only Crown Prince

22:30.790 --> 22:32.740
of Great Xia.

22:33.350 --> 22:34.200
Yes.

22:37.270 --> 22:39.170
If you have some free time,

22:39.680 --> 22:40.830
go see him

22:41.830 --> 22:43.550
and check his studies.

22:44.640 --> 22:46.480
Things are unpredictable.

22:47.110 --> 22:48.790
If anything happens,

22:49.310 --> 22:50.680
the Crown Prince

22:51.440 --> 22:53.970
may have to take over the throne
temporarily.

22:54.070 --> 22:55.640
It's better to be prepared

22:56.100 --> 22:57.140
in advance.

23:04.310 --> 23:05.510
Why are you laughing?

23:08.310 --> 23:11.430
[Be Remembered with Honor for All Ages]

23:09.880 --> 23:11.300
Why are you laughing?

23:23.800 --> 23:25.000
Mother,

23:28.180 --> 23:29.930
did you suddenly say this today

23:34.400 --> 23:36.070
because you think

23:37.070 --> 23:38.310
he can now replace me

23:39.660 --> 23:41.310
as your new puppet?

23:43.840 --> 23:45.170
Are you out of your mind?

23:49.060 --> 23:50.470
You don't actually think

23:52.440 --> 23:55.500
I would develop any fatherly affection
for him, do you?

23:57.710 --> 23:58.890
What do you mean?

24:07.920 --> 24:09.850
Where is the Imperial Astronomer?

24:12.000 --> 24:12.830
I am here.

24:13.680 --> 24:15.110
Check the feng shui

24:16.230 --> 24:17.430
of the lower palaces,

24:18.510 --> 24:19.510
the sacred paths,

24:20.970 --> 24:23.020
and the stele pavilions nearby.

24:24.510 --> 24:25.440
Look carefully.

24:27.270 --> 24:28.730
There must be no mistakes.

24:31.750 --> 24:32.590
Y-Yes,

24:33.200 --> 24:34.000
Your Majesty.

24:41.830 --> 24:43.070
Did you intercept any news?

24:43.070 --> 24:43.910
Ma'am,

24:44.130 --> 24:46.160
we have been stationed here
for a long time,

24:46.160 --> 24:48.960
but no urgent messages
have arrived from the city.

24:50.020 --> 24:51.350
It's already this hour.

24:51.920 --> 24:53.720
Lord Mu should have acted by now.

24:54.440 --> 24:56.170
How could there be no movement?

25:27.240 --> 25:27.790
Guards!

25:43.240 --> 25:43.960
Kill!

25:49.790 --> 25:51.180
Why are they here?

25:51.590 --> 25:53.850
Didn't Mu Yun send men to intercept them?

26:14.920 --> 26:15.900
Assassins!

26:16.550 --> 26:18.610
Send the Imperial Guards for backup!

26:19.350 --> 26:20.520
Assassins!

26:21.350 --> 26:23.410
Send the Imperial Guards for backup!

26:33.610 --> 26:35.870
They... they're really killing people!

26:44.840 --> 26:46.570
I wonder if His Majesty is safe.

26:49.750 --> 26:51.070
His Majesty is in danger.

26:51.070 --> 26:51.930
As his subject,

26:53.390 --> 26:54.390
I must go save him.

26:54.790 --> 26:55.190
Right.

27:08.350 --> 27:10.740
What is this guy made of?

27:10.830 --> 27:12.580
Iron and steel?

27:13.000 --> 27:14.550
Judging by your fighting skill,

27:14.550 --> 27:17.550
you must be Tu'er,
the top fighter of Yan State, right?

27:17.750 --> 27:18.550
That's right.

27:19.330 --> 27:21.860
I'm here to take
the Great Xia Emperor's head!

27:22.960 --> 27:23.860
Who are you?

27:24.030 --> 27:25.810
I'm just an ordinary servant

27:25.880 --> 27:27.830
in the palace of Great Xia.

27:28.440 --> 27:30.440
You people of Great Xia are all talk!

27:30.920 --> 27:31.780
Bring it on!

27:32.750 --> 27:33.240
Come on.

27:50.510 --> 27:51.440
What's that?

27:51.480 --> 27:54.610
Nine Heavens Mystical Fire Repeating
Sleeve Crossbow!

27:57.310 --> 27:57.990
Today,

27:58.480 --> 27:59.350
either you die,

27:59.830 --> 28:00.800
or I do.

28:08.920 --> 28:10.210
And who are you?

28:10.690 --> 28:12.020
Mind your own business.

28:23.000 --> 28:24.130
Everyone, close in!

28:24.200 --> 28:24.940
He can't aim!

28:56.200 --> 28:58.270
Yeah, his aim's awful.

29:14.680 --> 29:16.050
Your Majesty, do it!

29:17.380 --> 29:18.510
Do it, Your Majesty!

29:18.830 --> 29:20.560
Your Majesty, watch your back!

29:23.160 --> 29:23.700
Dan.

29:28.100 --> 29:29.560
What is it, Your Highness?

29:29.880 --> 29:30.410
Nothing.

29:30.790 --> 29:31.520
Keep moving.

30:32.590 --> 30:32.920
Dan.

30:33.400 --> 30:34.060
How are you?

30:34.350 --> 30:34.940
Mr. Bei.

30:47.210 --> 30:47.650
Stop!

30:48.000 --> 30:48.880
Restricted royal grounds.

30:48.880 --> 30:50.210
No unauthorized entry!

30:56.680 --> 30:57.190
[Token]

30:57.640 --> 30:58.770
It's our own people.

30:59.290 --> 31:00.300
What are you doing here?

31:00.300 --> 31:03.920
[Token]

31:00.720 --> 31:02.120
His Highness assigned us

31:02.310 --> 31:03.590
to go up the mountain immediately.

31:03.590 --> 31:04.120
Make way.

31:05.310 --> 31:06.110
Let them pass.

31:15.110 --> 31:15.770
Over there!

31:43.280 --> 31:43.860
Mr. Yang?

31:44.680 --> 31:45.540
Your Highness?

31:45.920 --> 31:47.000
What are you doing here?

31:47.000 --> 31:48.000
It's a long story.

31:48.400 --> 31:49.310
How are things on your side?

31:49.310 --> 31:51.240
His Majesty is trapped at the mausoleum.

31:51.240 --> 31:51.810
The forest

31:51.810 --> 31:53.790
is filled with Prince Duan's ambushers.

31:53.790 --> 31:56.070
I tried to go down the mountain
to fetch the Imperial Guards,

31:56.070 --> 31:57.620
but was pursued by the ambushers.

31:57.620 --> 31:59.640
Thank you for saving me just now,
Your Highness.

31:59.640 --> 32:00.500
Your Highness!

32:01.960 --> 32:02.490
Bad news!

32:02.590 --> 32:03.920
Someone is catching up.

32:04.880 --> 32:05.510
Mr. Yang.

32:05.720 --> 32:06.920
Run east through the forest,

32:06.920 --> 32:07.920
then head down the mountain. Hurry!

32:07.920 --> 32:08.510
Your Highness,

32:08.510 --> 32:09.790
what... what about you?

32:09.790 --> 32:11.000
Don't worry, Mr. Yang.

32:11.000 --> 32:11.750
I have a plan.

32:13.780 --> 32:14.450
Mr. Yang.

32:15.160 --> 32:16.320
The safety of His Majesty

32:16.320 --> 32:17.400
and the future of Great Xia

32:17.400 --> 32:18.600
are entrusted to you.

32:19.070 --> 32:21.670
You must bring the Imperial Guards
to save him.

32:22.190 --> 32:22.640
I

32:23.660 --> 32:24.190
am going!

32:27.240 --> 32:27.900
Xiahou Dan.

32:28.630 --> 32:29.690
I'll be there soon.

32:30.400 --> 32:31.160
Hold on.

32:32.030 --> 32:32.690
I have to...

32:33.590 --> 32:34.580
hold on.

33:00.680 --> 33:01.760
There is someone

33:04.270 --> 33:05.670
waiting for me to go back.

33:11.660 --> 33:13.820
Zhang San's Diary.

34:51.590 --> 34:56.360
Long live the Emperor!

35:00.230 --> 35:01.400
You may rise.
